{"tid":1394953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"TurboJet員工與香港人共同進退","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T14:31:17.000Z","uid":237601,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1eac61297d87e5e8cf8af8821c1fca65d8a73c20","tid":1394953,"uid":237601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"《信德中旅船務有限公司噴射飛航員工聯署信》<br />\n<br />\n致 林鄭月娥及其政府官員：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一班關心社會的噴射飛航員工。連日來，本港不同專業團體、政府部門及公營機構員工均先後就《逃犯條例》修訂引起的連串爭議發聲，現在我們亦藉此聯署信表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n過去兩個月，數以百萬計市民汗流浹背走上街頭，表達反對《逃犯條例》修訂，甚至有市民以死相諫，但政府依然故我，拒絕正面回應，並以「暫緩」、「壽終正寢」等語言偽術意圖蒙騙全港市民；同時，政府縱容警方濫用暴力，不合理地以催淚彈、布袋彈、橡膠子彈及海綿彈等對付示威者，甚至是記者、議員及救護義工，這是完全不能接受的。<br />\n <br />\n守護香港，是身為香港人的義務。我們希望真正與青年同行，守護他們所堅守的香港的核心價值。<br />\n現促請政府正面回應市民五大訴求:<br />\n<br />\n一 : 徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n二 : 收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n三 : 撤銷對所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n四 : 徹底追究警隊濫權情況 (成立獨立調查委員會)<br />\n<br />\n五 : 立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n同熱愛這片土地的噴射飛航員工  敬上<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kbcegBf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkbcegBf.jpg&h=5360763f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrZsHV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrZsHV.jpg&h=45245980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzOhenW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzOhenW.jpg&h=bfdedadd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJE4DPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJE4DPC.jpg&h=9b2967fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d3Nt5uC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd3Nt5uC.jpg&h=7e297a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p9ajsHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp9ajsHY.jpg&h=0cec79e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rpwVLuD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrpwVLuD.jpg&h=b7f76d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/omgyw9E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fomgyw9E.jpg&h=e8f7f837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EwiH9Wk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwiH9Wk.jpg&h=8107c00b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWKXen0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWKXen0.jpg&h=71557d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8abq7H1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8abq7H1.jpg&h=4393f998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y890WBm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy890WBm.jpg&h=0d5582cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KyD85uH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKyD85uH.jpg&h=09043ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w4OALuH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw4OALuH.jpg&h=8c277ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gk0vzn3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGk0vzn3.jpg&h=e4c63959&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c75cefc1029976fe03bea2d37982b60e65c1b75","tid":1394953,"uid":237601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:10:14.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"eb5a33ee0cbddf088eea0100a917798a5cbcb356","tid":1394953,"uid":255784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0b7435b9427e095df0c8607c12204a156b44e75","tid":1394953,"uid":255784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ab38e2f8a4c0c0fb88470207b3bde92449a7ac4","tid":1394953,"uid":142452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":